            p.section-label For the men of affairs it is very important to be always on time! For people who drive around town a lot for personal or business purposes.<br><br>We offer a service of personal driver, who will accompany you all day long and wait for you in a convenient location.  <br><br>Moving around, frequent business trips, business meetings, parking in the center of the city on weekdays - ceases to be a problem, while using the services of a personal driver.
