            p.section-title Corporate taxi
            p.section-label Professional solution for your transport issues! <br><br>Profitable offer for organizations and companies that haven’t got personal fleet, will allow businesses to save on logistics and take off all the worries related to transportation.<br><br>Supplying services to corporate clients, we consider almost all customers requirements: Vehicle class, type of transportation, reporting on routes, time & cost of services, the ability to receive data with a GPS-module to check the route and time on the road.
