        .column.one
            p.section-title Auto-nanny
            p.section-label Auto-nanny – is a personal driver for your child. We provide competent assistance to parents in the safe transportation of children, rather than bring the children to the specified address.
                <br><br>This service is somewhat different from the standard taxi services, so as a function of the driver is not only transportation, but also the transfer of the child in the hands of the responsible person, informing parents about location, moving and other related information about the child.
                <br><br>Personal child's driver met him at the entrance / apartment and take him to school, kindergarten or sports section, and then returns to parents.
                <br><br>We protect your children as well as our own, because children - is the most valuable thing we have!
        .column.two.illustration(style="background-image: url(http://www.keenthemes.com/preview/metronic/theme/assets/global/plugins/jcrop/demos/demo_files/image2.jpg)")
