            p.section-label "Etalon Taxi" has at its disposal minibuses Mercedes, VW and Mitsubishi from 6 to 27 seats for services to delegations, conferences and other corporate events.
                <br><br>You can order a minibus for any occasions: weddings, corporate trips, family travel and so forth.
